Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.24,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:21.31,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.98,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我脚步不停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:38.94,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有双脚的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:42.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知晓走过的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:49.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我期待着漫漫长夜后的绝美风景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:52.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}活在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:58.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神之灵峰 新绿宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:03.26,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟深处 苍穹尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:09.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要一一到达 永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:12.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要走遍每一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:16.02,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}早安 世界
